### 1. Route Structure Patterns

#### Module Organization
Routes are organized in `/apps/api/src/modules/` with one folder per feature:
- `/modules/agents/` → agents.routes.ts (+ helper files like agent-auth.helper.ts)
- `/modules/wallets/` → wallets.routes.ts
- `/modules/auth/` → auth.routes.ts (+ services: telegram-auth.service.ts)
- `/modules/quests/` → quests.routes.ts (+ multiple services)
